{"title":"教师画像礼赞","authors":["陈伯吹"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":9,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"教师画像礼赞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯吹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老师，您好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在街心花园的中央，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您那高大闪光的画像，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹如挺立的青松百丈；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浅草铺在您脚下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜花围绕您身旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清风吹送您沁人肺腑的芬芳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老师，您好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您那慈祥和蔼的脸庞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑意浮漾在微启的唇上；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明净的镜片后面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有秀丽的慧眼一双，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透视着少年儿童的心房。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老师，您好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这街心花园旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成千上万地人来人往，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个个怀着虔诚的意愿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向您行个注目礼——无限敬仰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感谢您长年日夜操心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了祖国儿女们的健康成长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老师，您好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您昂首阔步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从容安详，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"评说古往今来的人物，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地理上山环海抱的雄壮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"科学上的理、化、声、光；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您的教鞭指挥若定，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指点祖国的锦锈前方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老师，您好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在街心花园的中央，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您的画像屹立如青翠的山冈："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天，太阳耀得银光雪亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜晚，电炬照得金色辉煌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您栉风沐雨日日年年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象指路的明灯放射光芒。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}